            . I am in the service of Messrs. Curtis and Company; they are <rs id="t18130407-108-viclabel554" type="occupation">biscuit bakers and flour merchants</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130407-108-victim995 t18130407-108-viclabel554"></join>
