               <p>Q. What are the names of the partners in the firm - A. Sir 
               <persName id="t18130407-108-person1001">
                  William 
                  Curtis
               <interp inst="t18130407-108-person1001" type="surname" value="Curtis"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130407-108-person1001" type="given" value="William"></interp>
